{"tid":895450,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"METAL BUILD 討論區 （16）繼續撚狗","createTime":"2018-11-09T08:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T04:14:39.000Z","uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"01af97e2abcccfd79c9c05906d0caa3a7e34d252","tid":895450,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"第 1 頁<br />\n#1FryingDog &bull; 8-28<br />\nMetal Build 系列常用資訊網：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sp.tamashii.jp/item_brand/metal_build\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsp.tamashii.jp%2Fitem_brand%2Fmetal_build&d=%2F14kkVbimtOb1dvr8Wj%2BqG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d2c5b047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sp.tamashii.jp/item_brand/metal_build</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入面有哂所有會出同出過既作品同出品年月份<br />\n（除左魂限OO Raiser)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ:何謂魂限？<br />\nA:經p-bandai 網上訂購的限定版<br />\n<br />\nQ:何謂魂展限？<br />\nA:每年日本秋葉原Tamashii Nation 展覽的會場限定版除左上面提個盒Trans-am OOR，全部都在展後推出相同的魂限<br />\n<br />\nQ:何謂普通販賣？<br />\nA:即就咁普通係鋪頭賣買既產品<br />\n<br />\nQ:咩版最好QC?<br />\nA:無論行、日、亞，QC都一樣，同為made in China<br />\n<br />\n常用訂購網：<br />\n<a href=\"http://amiami.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famiami.com&d=%2F14kkVbimtOb1dvr8Wj%2BqG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f80a778d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://amiami.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://1999.co.jp/eng/gundam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1999.co.jp%2Feng%2Fgundam&d=%2F14kkVbimtOb1dvr8Wj%2BqG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=024a2132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://1999.co.jp/eng/gundam</a><br />\n<br />\n魂限網頁：<br />\n<a href=\"http://p-bandai.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp-bandai.hk&d=%2F14kkVbimtOb1dvr8Wj%2BqG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1cc64af4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://p-bandai.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://p-bandai.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp-bandai.jp&d=%2F14kkVbimtOb1dvr8Wj%2BqG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=bc14b940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://p-bandai.jp</a><br />\n<br />\nF91 Q &amp;A<br />\nQ:換頭要連個長方體換 好撚難除<br />\nA:除BACKPACK就得<br />\n<br />\nQ:插落去個架度個兩粒野係邊度<br />\nA:主體盒 右下角 透明袋入面<br />\n<br />\nQ:兩邊肩有虛位<br />\nA:睇說明書，有得拍返埋<br />\n<br />\nQ:邊度買<br />\nA:精品孤仔睡記<br />\n<br />\nQ:買日定行<br />\nA:無分別<br />\n<br />\nQ: OOQ用咩電<br />\nA: LR41*2<br />\n<br />\nQ: exia 點分初版再版<br />\nA:初版左下角logo行字有多一個&lsquo;MBS&rsquo; ,再版係無既<br />\n<br />\nQ: freedom 點分初版再版<br />\nA: 初版紫再版藍（未有實質證據支持）<br />\n<br />\nQ: xxx依家個價抵唔抵<br />\nA: 有愛就買啦屌你<br />\n<br />\nQ: 女神手軟點算<br />\nA: 未過7日就send 返比睡記換"},{"pid":"f6526edb6cd1eb5f67556bc089e4673918e33957","tid":895450,"uid":6874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"入左F91,紅迷改,突擊同新SF<br />\n幾時再販埋Destiny<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441253d0a3b1a2c7834016bc5a3b0b6000638f8e","tid":895450,"uid":47287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6526edb6cd1eb5f67556bc089e4673918e33957","tid":895450,"uid":6874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"入左F91,紅迷改,突擊同新SF<br />\n幾時再販埋Destiny<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"呢家呢個價唔使等再版啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd02111ae7da7c71a78a49a9d7f54e1a16fe280b","tid":895450,"uid":6874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"441253d0a3b1a2c7834016bc5a3b0b6000638f8e","tid":895450,"uid":47287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6526edb6cd1eb5f67556bc089e4673918e33957","tid":895450,"uid":6874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"入左F91,紅迷改,突擊同新SF<br />\n幾時再販埋Destiny<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"呢家呢個價唔使等再版啦